---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="博客 | AJMD">
  <section style="padding: 2rem 0;">
    <h1>博客</h1>
    <p style="color:#888; margin-bottom:2rem;">AI+财务的实操经验、效率方法和踩坑记录。</p>

    <div class="card blog-card">
      <p class="date">2026-05-13</p>
      <h3><a href="/blog/ai-duizhang">以前觉得AI做账不靠谱，现在真香了</a></h3>
      <p>发票整理、报销审核、月结差异——3个复制粘贴就能用的AI场景。</p>
      <span class="tag">AI财务</span>
      <span class="tag">实操</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card blog-card">
      <p class="date">2026-05-12</p>
      <h3><a href="/blog/excel-vs-ai">做了5年财务才明白：Excel再6，不如会问AI</a></h3>
      <p>3个AI提问公式，让工作效率翻倍。</p>
      <span class="tag">AI财务</span>
      <span class="tag">提示词</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card blog-card">
      <p class="date">2026-05-09</p>
      <h3><a href="/blog/3-duizhang-moban">3个AI提示词搞定银行对账</a></h3>
      <p>从2小时到3分钟，对账差异分析的AI模板。</p>
      <span class="tag">对账</span>
      <span class="tag">模板</span>
    </div>

    <div class="card blog-card">
      <p class="date">2026-05-09</p>
      <h3><a href="/blog/jiejie-8h-2h">月底结账从8小时→2小时，我用了3个AI提示词</a></h3>
      <p>月结效率提升4倍的核心方法。</p>
      <span class="tag">月结</span>
      <span class="tag">效率</span>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:1rem;">
      <p style="color:#555; font-size:0.9rem;">更多文章更新中...</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
